   \"startedAt\": 1773000487424,\n      \"endedAt\": 1773000537097\n    }\n  ],\n  \"text\": \"active subagents:\\n1. 小说评审-人物分析师 (glm-5, 1m) running - 阅读 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/novel-reviews/prompt-2026-03-08T20-0...\\n\\nrecent (last 30m):\\n2. 小说评审-设定管理员 (glm-5, 1m, tokens 3.1k (in 3.0k / out 68), prompt/cache 10k) failed - 阅读 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/novel-reviews/prompt-2026-03-08T20-0...\\n3. 小说评审-逻辑审核员 (glm-5, 1m, tokens 12k (in 10k / out 1.7k), prompt/cache 14k) done - 阅读 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/novel-reviews/prompt-2026-03-08T20-0...\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"ok","action":"list","requesterSessionKey":"agent:main:cron:146083a3-dae7-409d-86cc-6a953d1cbdd6","callerSessionKey":"agent:main:cron:146083a3-dae7-409d-86cc-6a953d1cbdd6","callerIsSubagent":false,"total":3,"active":[{"index":1,"runId":"289f85cd-cecd-4338-824e-d629887cf1e5","sessionKey":"agent:main:subagent:cb9462d1-9675-4aaa-9535-da1c64e4eddd","label":"小说评审-人物分析师","task":"阅读 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/novel-reviews/prompt-2026-03-08T20-0...","status":"running","runtime":"1m","runtimeMs":41377,"model":"zai/glm-5","startedAt":1773000502292}],"recent":[{"index":2,"runId":"1e4276fc-d168-4f57-8f51-958f97a40f65","sessionKey":"agent:main:subagent:35ca1b5c-2a05-464c-ab9f-cba6481aa3da","label":"小说评审-设定管理员","task":"阅读 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/novel-reviews/prompt-2026-03-08T20-0...","status":"failed","runtime":"1m","runtimeMs":3399,"model":"zai/glm-5","totalTokens":10152,"startedAt":1773000527517,"endedAt":1773000530916},{"index":3,"runId":"23c7cf09-f661-4cb1-b5b9-67e66d2a221d","sessionKey":"agent:main:subagent:60b7e44e-72d1-4253-84a9-6afef7e42201","label":"小说评审-逻辑审核员","task":"阅读 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/novel-reviews/prompt-2026-03-08T20-0...","status":"done","runtime":"1m","runtimeMs":49673,"model":"zai/glm-5","totalTokens":13895,"startedAt":1773000487424,"endedAt":1773000537097}],"text":"active subagents:\n1. 小说评审-人物分析师 (glm-5, 1m) running - 阅读 /root/.opencla